# Build
$ make

# How to Run
$ cd bin
$ ./assign


# Options in application
Seen has three object
1) WireMesh teapot
2) FilledMesh teapot
3) FilledMesh Cube

To Select object
Press 1: WireMesh teapot
Press 2: FilledMesh teapot
Press 3: FilledMesh Cube

By default Object 1 (WireMesh is selected)

To Rotate FilledMesh Cude
Press 3
To Scale
+ : increase size
- : Decrease size

To Rotate
x : Rotate on x axis
y : Rotate on y axis
z : Rotate on z axis

To Move
Arrow up : Move upwards
Arrow Down: Move downwards
Arrow left: Move Left
Arrow right: Move Right
